t\">\n1239 |                             Fully compliant under sovereign regional regulation patterns. Hardware enclaves lock memory access keys dynamically.\n1240 |                           </p>\n1241 |                         </div>\n1242 |                         <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304] space-y-2\">\n1243 |                           <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#009DFF] uppercase tracking-wider block font-bold\">ZERO-TRUST AUDIT LOGS</span>\n1244 |                           <p className=\"text-xs text-white/80 font-light\">\n1245 |                             Immutable logging layer writes SHA-256 block receipts for each transaction without persisting PII attributes locally.\n1246 |                           </p>\n1247 |                         </div>\n1248 |                         <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304] space-y-2\">\n1249 |                           <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-amber-400 uppercase tracking-wider block font-bold\">MODEL DRIFT GUARD</span>\n1250 |                           <p className=\"text-xs text-white/80 font-light\">\n1251 |                             Continuous compliance score filters and mitigates potential hallucination patterns down to less than 0.01% standard.\n1252 |                           </p>\n1253 |                         </div>\n1254 |                         <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#030304] space-y-2\">\n1255 |                           <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-wider block font-bold\">VIRTUAL PRIVATE CANOPY</span>\n1256 |                           <p className=\"text-xs text-white/80 font-light\">\n1257 |                             Isolated VPC boundary blockages deny any unencrypted internet egress during agent transaction routing tasks.\n1258 |                           </p>\n1259 |                         </div>\n1260 |  